<li dir="ltr"><strong>Chemotherapy:</strong> <a href="https:///generics/carboplatin-209514?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Stomach cancer_factbox_0_treatment_6_direct_link_0">Carboplatin</a>, <a href="https:///generics/cisplatin-209610?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Stomach cancer_factbox_0_treatment_6_direct_link_1">Cisplatin</a>, <a href="https:///generics/capecitabine-209498?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Stomach cancer_factbox_0_treatment_6_direct_link_2">Capecitabine</a>, <a href="https:///generics/docetaxel-209753?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Stomach cancer_factbox_0_treatment_6_direct_link_3">docetaxel</a>, and <a href="https:///generics/fluorouracil-209896?utm_source=disease_page&amp;utm_medium=Stomach cancer_factbox_0_treatment_6_direct_link_4">Fluorouracil</a></li>
